Stadium Ticket RESTful API for Linux/Unix

0.  To install prerequisite packages as root:

    ./install-prerequisites.sh

1.  To initialize database schema:

    scripts/mysql.sh <sql/schema.sql

2.  To run unit tests:

    scripts/mysql.sh <sql/reset.sql
    ./test_tickets.py

3.  To start app:

    ./app.py

4.  To test app:

    ./app-test.sh

5.  To load test app:

    ./load-test.sh

6. To build a Docker container:

    docker-compose up --build
